rural /ˈrʊərəl/

1. ADJ Rural places are far away from large towns or cities. 乡村的 

例： These plants have a tendency to grow in the more rural areas. 这些植物倾向于生长在更偏远的乡村地区。 

2. ADJ Rural means having features which are typical of areas that are far away from large towns or cities. 有乡村特色的 [ADJ n] 

例： ...the old rural way of life. …古老的乡村生活方式。

</div>

